## Theme Var Field

A field that captures a structured theme variable (used by the brand-guide system)

### Usage

```ts
import { CardDef, field, contains } from 'https://cardstack.com/base/card-api';
import ThemeVarField from 'https://cardstack.com/base/structured-theme-variables';

export class Example extends CardDef {
  @field themeVars = contains(ThemeVarField);
}
```
